  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d0b62a0-569a-4669-93ce-f6dc4468dcf0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-33ecf5da-a7c2-46c5-a30d-0f17994e9a85\"><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e8a3f26f-eba8-4dd2-ba5b-e6f53115dc93\"><b>안녕하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-48f6b2f3-b5a5-4d5c-be99-e36809f2dffe\"><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-eee0141f-bae2-4f9c-bef7-fa164242822d\"><b>평일 야간진료, 주말진료가 가능한</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-252f21f0-98a2-4393-bfff-2280a8925650\"><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#98d36c;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1a67118e-df1f-4e61-8b74-13f2b27ca9ee\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-dd4fe4a4-db3b-408c-bb9b-529f07ca12b0\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6d0b62a0-569a-4669-93ce-f6dc4468dcf0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f909b50-97c6-47af-855c-03ea8412540a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"1\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_1.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b219d22-6583-451c-944e-13818320e439\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-458bfba5-125b-4d45-8c9d-9db60140203f\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-10786ae1-79a2-4a85-9e5c-6b3f72387a97\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-813bded0-3365-45ab-9813-e845c8f28926\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a65375d1-8baf-418f-a935-980f56508b25\"><b>기혈 순환이 건강을 좌우합니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-018a6ddd-c43b-4a86-8787-4282d947693b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-feae3aa6-2781-45ab-9c52-4586c77a09f3\">한의학에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-09aa9dd8-d3a1-4db7-895e-69f9205530b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2fe87cae-6a38-4a1a-9af2-ff1c8302bdc6\"><b>‘기혈(氣血)’이 순조롭게 흐르는 것</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6acf659a-5dfa-42e0-9b74-0aafd88de5e1\">을 건강의 기본으로 봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da7eae02-1f64-4145-89eb-8f86e26bb5fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-aadaf44c-db67-4e49-9b92-d6fda86285be\">‘기(氣)’는 생명 에너지, ‘혈(血)’은 몸을 구성하고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-76ae4eee-8bc0-424b-b3f3-72db872121e1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f5163618-b696-4a45-bf43-2b938d262bdd\">영양을 공급하는 피라고 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-25304c95-5dca-4439-b3f9-ba0519d96695\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b4fbf71f-a82f-4bce-8e9a-c2ff68184692\">이 두 가지가 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0ac4d81a-e604-49cd-9617-0cae708daee7\"><b>전신을 고르게 순환</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-aa02558b-238c-457c-958e-2ff20ae57f22\">하지 못하면 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7bb7cb14-8696-4040-92a6-2dac35fb5bf0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8c61b5d7-e848-4775-b2bd-bbbc3d3873bf\">각종 통증과 질환이 생길 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4b219d22-6583-451c-944e-13818320e439\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-90436500-ede4-482f-9891-a5fcb620ea3d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a08d310d-f95d-4b5a-9e1e-c35ec03dadc3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a08d310d-f95d-4b5a-9e1e-c35ec03dadc3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/97415c5dcf1a9576.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/97415c5dcf1a9576.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/97415c5dcf1a9576.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a08d310d-f95d-4b5a-9e1e-c35ec03dadc3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-48a4af6b-daa9-4726-92a9-f5943a01381d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-268ea576-93fd-4731-8507-ce85b7c342fe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d223e95b-3709-45f3-873e-98d08909a85b\"><b>기혈이 막히면 어떤 문제가 생기나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-85b786c1-3a89-48c1-9eb8-c30b632f2f41\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ba937c3-cff2-482c-9eeb-577e426d1b6d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4932a4be-997a-4cd5-8f1e-589c7e9a6740\"><b>통증</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b99b1af7-3ad0-4339-9353-3a5250980ccf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-66d73a26-7f85-455f-bd7c-6681e04db2f1\">한의학에 “不通則痛(통하지 않으면 아프다)”는 말이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ac3c02fb-224d-417d-bc15-641ff5d238a2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-49dcd93c-bd88-4140-8a2e-049a1b0282c3\">근육통, 관절통, 편두통 등은 기혈이 막혀 생기는 대표적인 증상입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5e82aa56-ee58-447d-adf4-66190e561667\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-47667306-94d4-47bb-8f27-9a4d8ac366d2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a1aeeb7-ae25-4551-809f-e2d4c3547dae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-658f24db-d704-4598-a323-b6eb66a97f7b\"><b>소화기 장애</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-92da48f1-5212-4591-b93e-50fa6af26358\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ca41af45-4c36-49f3-b32f-21dee2bcb7dc\">위장에 기혈이 몰리거나 부족하면 소화불량, 식욕부진, 속쓰림 등이 생길 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae1a9cb9-f2e2-4f44-ab0a-369f9e74f537\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3f2e96a4-6625-4162-9eef-0aec5a743701\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-19d182fa-8ab1-4a4f-a3a3-fc34034c0348\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cc7ca376-404d-40e2-beda-475b88dc56a9\"><b>면역력 저하</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94b52f3c-fa8a-4b6e-9831-bcfd9011e82e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-21d0ba46-ca42-4121-9b12-b77a0c6ddd7a\">기는 몸을 방어하는 에너지원입니다. 기가 약하거나 순환이 잘 안 되면 쉽게 피로해지고 잔병치레를 자주 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f1ae2315-2ebe-4932-ac3e-d3fcdca12258\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c35b264a-d9f5-4819-87bf-2b2927a12684\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0b00f8a8-9029-49bc-9982-9aa273e34dcb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-84e7164f-b71e-4db1-bc6e-6c7a5d9a44f2\"><b>정서적 불안정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5b0e63aa-95cf-4ac0-9c99-d78cc69ce879\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4ca2fb90-fb52-4b6e-902d-a692ddbe9daa\">기혈 순환은 심신에도 영향을 미칩니다. 우울감, 불면, 짜증 등의 증상은 기혈 불균형에서 비롯될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-85b786c1-3a89-48c1-9eb8-c30b632f2f41\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f89b49dd-3da7-4acc-8ba1-fbd3f84edfe5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f89b49dd-3da7-4acc-8ba1-fbd3f84edfe5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a90615504ee9aee7.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a90615504ee9aee7.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a90615504ee9aee7.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"750\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-f89b49dd-3da7-4acc-8ba1-fbd3f84edfe5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9ff36328-fbbe-4fe2-b9ad-6cb635cd5382\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-c2083fef-513e-404b-ad96-61ab0e85afff\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a825db95-933f-4d06-b5ad-6c4a85832367\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38cb6370-99f2-44ec-971d-74533933301d\"><b>기혈 순환이 잘 되게 하려면?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b6c55eb4-4ef9-4fd9-b28b-b3915b3cb8cd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eafb44ac-e2be-4d56-9887-e284d73f514e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9802234c-af6e-4769-a207-f9e9c9cf82d2\"><b>침·뜸 치료</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0dc90345-2368-4502-b48a-749ee478107b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-66e73dae-14e1-4d4f-bb64-dc146e165ba9\">→ 기혈의 흐름을 자극해 막힌 곳을 풀어주는 대표적인 방법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5245a7b2-3979-4795-9789-2d755dafbe34\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7314f1f1-66fc-436c-a243-931b6b622a94\"><b>한약 복용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-820a29d6-2af6-4053-a87f-ed1d558981df\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d453c5f6-19f2-4a28-8e93-900387b4c578\">→ 기혈이 허하거나 막힌 곳에 따라 맞춤 한약으로 균형을 조절합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2dbf4ebc-7127-4010-b68c-bc9ee95f4c9a\"><span style=\"\" cla